These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, metal, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | metal | pop |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, bird, hedgehog
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the hedgehog is in the middle##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Pet   | rabbit | hedgehog | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, motorbike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Transport   | motorbike | trike | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks, singing
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Hobby   | chess | magic-tricks | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
