.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery, satire
1. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | mystery | satire |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
