.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | sudoku | dancing |

